OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FHousing and Planning Minister, Matthew
OL,8,FPennycook, told political
OL,9,Fcorrespondent Kit Bradshaw, "companies
OL,10,Fcannot profit for failure".
OL,12,FThames Water has been fined #122.7
OL,13,Fmillion after two investigations into
OL,14,Fwastewater and dividend payments, in
OL,15,Fthe largest penalty Ofwat has ever
OL,16,Fissued, the regulator said.
