OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FThe water giant will pay #104.5
OL,8,Fmillion for breaches of rules relating
OL,9,Fto its wastewater operations, after
OL,10,FOfwat said it "failed to protect the
OL,11,Fenvironment".
OL,13,FOfwat chief executive David Black
OL,14,Fsaid: "Our investigation has uncovered
OL,15,Fa series of failures by the company to
OL,16,Fbuild, maintain and operate adequate
OL,17,Finfrastructure to meet its obligations.
