OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,F"The company also failed to come up
OL,8,Fwith an acceptable redress package
OL,9,Fthat would have benefited the
OL,10,Fenvironment, so we have imposed a
OL,11,Fsignificant financial penalty."
OL,13,FThames Water will pay an extra #18.2
OL,14,Fmillion for breaking rules related to
OL,15,Fdividend payments, the first ever
OL,16,Fdividend-related fine, Ofwat said.
OL,18,FThe watchdog pointed to dividends of
OL,19,F#37.5 million in October 2023 and
OL,20,F#131.3 million in March 2024.
