OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FThe firm is currently in a "cash lock-
OL,8,Fup" period and no more dividends can
OL,9,Fbe paid without approval from the
OL,10,Fregulator.
OL,12,FMr Black added: "We will not stand by
OL,13,Fwhen companies pay undeserved
OL,14,Fdividends to their shareholders."
OL,16,FOfwat said the money will be paid by
OL,17,Fthe utility giant and its investors,
OL,18,Fnot by customers.
