OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,8,F"The era of profiting from failure is
OL,9,Fover. The Government is cleaning up
OL,10,Four rivers, lakes and seas for good."
OL,12,FThe wastewater fine was first proposed
OL,13,Flast year and confirmed on Wednesday.
OL,15,FA Thames Water spokesperson said: "We
OL,16,Ftake our responsibility towards the
OL,17,Fenvironment very seriously and note
OL,18,Fthat Ofwat acknowledges we have
OL,19,Falready made progress to address
OL,20,Fissues raised in the investigation
OL,21,Frelating to storm overflows.
