OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FMike Keil, chief executive of the
OL,8,FConsumer Council for Water, said:
OL,9,F"These failures amount to a serious
OL,10,Fbetrayal of customers and the
OL,11,Fenvironment by Thames Water and come
OL,12,Fat a time when our research shows it
OL,13,Fis already the least trusted water
OL,14,Fcompany in England and Wales.
OL,16,F"We're pleased to see Ofwat using its
OL,17,Fnew powers to block unjustified
OL,18,Fdividends, which shareholders should
OL,19,Fhave to earn through the company
OL,20,Fdelivering on its commitments to
OL,21,Fcustomers and the environment.
